OL,3,CPensioner killed by psychiatric
OL,4,Cpatient 'failed on every level', says
OL,5,Cfamily
OL,7,FThe family of a pensioner who was
OL,8,Fstabbed to death by a woman who fled
OL,9,Fan acute mental health unit have said
OL,10,Ftheir "nightmare never ends", and they
OL,11,Fwere "failed on every level" by two
OL,12,Fpolice forces and one NHS trust.
OL,14,FA coroner ruled on Thursday that 74-
OL,15,Fyear-old Roger Leadbeater was
OL,16,Funlawfully killed, after patient Emma
OL,17,FBorowy was permitted to go on leave,
OL,18,Fwhen this request would have probably
OL,19,Fbeen rejected if procedures had been
OL,20,Ffollowed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/20
