OL,3,CPensioner killed by psychiatric
OL,4,Cpatient 'failed on every level', says
OL,5,Cfamily
OL,7,FRetired bus driver Roger was stabbed
OL,8,Fmultiple times by Emma Borowy, 32, as
OL,9,Fhe walked his dog Max in a Sheffield
OL,10,Fpark in August 2023.
OL,12,FThe pensioner suffered a total of 75
OL,13,Fsharp-force injuries, his dog refused
OL,14,Fto leave his side after he died.
OL,16,FHis family has told ITV News that they
OL,17,Fwant a public inquiry.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/20
