OL,3,CPensioner killed by psychiatric
OL,4,Cpatient 'failed on every level', says
OL,5,Cfamily
OL,7,FThe inquest previously heard that
OL,8,FBorowy, who had paranoid
OL,9,Fschizophrenia, had absconded from her
OL,10,Fward nine times, attempted to abscond
OL,11,Fa further 15 times, and failed to
OL,12,Freturn from leave three times.
OL,14,FDespite this, Borowy was still
OL,15,Fpermitted escorted leave, two days
OL,16,Fbefore Roger was attacked, when staff
OL,17,Fat Greater Manchester Mental Health
OL,18,FNHS Foundation Trust failed to follow
OL,19,Ftheir own policies and did not have an
OL,20,Faccurate risk assessment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/20
