OL,4,Cpatient 'failed on every level', says
OL,5,Cfamily
OL,7,FCoroner Tanyka Rawden concluded "it is
OL,8,Flikely the risk factors would have
OL,9,Fbeen too high and leave would not have
OL,10,Fbeen granted" if the procedures had
OL,11,Fbeen properly followed.
OL,13,FRawden also criticised the procedures
OL,14,Fof both Greater Manchester and South
OL,15,FYorkshire police forces when dealing
OL,16,Fwith handovers of vulnerable missing
OL,17,Fpeople.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/20
