OL,7,FA Prevention of Future Deaths (PFD)
OL,8,Freport has been issued to Greater
OL,9,FManchester Police and South Yorkshire
OL,10,FPolice. They must respond with
OL,11,Fproposed actions to prevent further
OL,12,Fdeaths from happening.
OL,14,FThe inquest heard how Borowy told
OL,15,Fpolice and psychiatrists she was
OL,16,F"tricked by the devil" into killing
OL,17,FRoger in a "ritual sacrifice", and had
OL,18,Fpreviously spoken to officers about
OL,19,F"murdering people" and causing a
OL,20,F"bloodbath".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/20
