OL,7,FShe later died in prison, four months
OL,8,Fafter the attack.
OL,10,FThe inquest heard that Borowy was
OL,11,Fsectioned in October 2022 after she
OL,12,Fwas arrested for killing two goats
OL,13,Fwith a knife.
OL,15,FHer flat also concerned police, who
OL,16,Ffound a "shrine of unicorns", teddy
OL,17,Fbears floating in the bath, plus a
OL,18,Fhammer and rope.
