OL,7,FBorowy first went Awol from the
OL,8,Fhospital ward on October 21 2022,
OL,9,Fescaping by smashing the window of her
OL,10,Froom.
OL,12,FShe absconded multiple times after
OL,13,Fthat, either escaping from the
OL,14,Fhospital or slipping from her escort
OL,15,Fwhile on supervised leave.
OL,17,FOn two occasions, she was carrying
OL,18,Fknives when she was found by police.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/20
