OL,7,FRawden said some of these incidents
OL,8,Fwere not known to those treating her
OL,9,Fat the hospital.
OL,11,FIn her conclusion, the coroner said a
OL,12,Frisk assessment was completed after
OL,13,FBorowy absconded on August 4 2023 and
OL,14,Fthreatened to kill her friend, but
OL,15,Fthis was "lacking in detail,
OL,16,Finaccurate, and missing important and
OL,17,Frelevant information".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/20
