OL,5,Cfamily
OL,7,FBorowy's care was then transferred to
OL,8,Fa new consultant on August 7 - two
OL,9,Fdays before the attack on Roger - and
OL,10,Fthe consultant authorised further
OL,11,Fleave during a meeting.
OL,13,FRawden said the authorisation of leave
OL,14,Fwas made ""without clear documentation
OL,15,Fof the reasons for the decision,
OL,16,Fwithout consideration of a detailed
OL,17,Frisk assessment, and outside of the
OL,18,Fpolicies which stated that leave after
OL,19,Fa suspension should be reviewed face-
OL,20,Fto-face at the next multi-disciplinary
OL,21,Fteam meeting".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/20
