OL,7,FShe added that this decision was "not
OL,8,Freasonable or proportionate".
OL,10,FRoger's niece, Angela Hector, said
OL,11,Fthose entrusted to keep Emma and the
OL,12,Fpublic safe "failed on every level".
OL,14,F"On the 9th of August 2023, our lives
OL,15,Fwere shattered forever.
OL,17,F"Roger was brutally attacked by a
OL,18,Fstranger while walking his beloved
OL,19,Fdog, Max.
