OL,5,Cfamily
OL,7,F"What happened that night was not just
OL,8,Fviolence. It was barbaric. Beyond
OL,9,Fcomprehension. Roger suffered 124
OL,10,Finjuries. He was stabbed through his
OL,11,Feye, his skull, his body torn apart.
OL,13,F"This was like a horror film. You
OL,14,Fcannot switch off. Except this is
OL,15,Freal. And this was Roger. Our Roger.
OL,16,FThe nightmares will never end.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/20
