OL,3,CPensioner killed by psychiatric
OL,4,Cpatient 'failed on every level', says
OL,5,Cfamily
OL,7,F"Those who are in positions of trust,
OL,8,FGreater Manchester Mental Health,
OL,9,FGreater Manchester Police and South
OL,10,FYorkshire Police, Emma Borowy put her
OL,11,Ftrust in you to keep her safe and well.
OL,13,F"The public put their trust in you to
OL,14,Fprotect us. You all failed on every
OL,15,Flevel.
OL,17,F"Roger will never come home. That
OL,18,Foutcome cannot change. But you must
OL,19,Fmake sure no other family suffers this
OL,20,Fdevastation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/20
