OL,4,Cpatient 'failed on every level', says
OL,5,Cfamily
OL,7,FIn a written statement, his family
OL,8,Fexpressed their disappointment that a
OL,9,FPrevention of Future Deaths (PFD)
OL,10,Freport was not issued to Greater
OL,11,FManchester Mental Health NHS
OL,12,FFoundation Trust.
OL,14,F"While we welcome this clear
OL,15,Facknowledgement of police failings, we
OL,16,Fremain profoundly disappointed that no
OL,17,FPFD has been issued to Greater
OL,18,FManchester Mental Health NHS
OL,19,FFoundation Trust. Emma Borowy was a
OL,20,Fknown inpatient under the Mental
OL,21,FHealth Act.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
