OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F319A1769188414
OL,3,CPensioner killed by psychiatric
OL,4,Cpatient 'failed on every level', says
OL,5,Cfamily
OL,7,F"She absconded repeatedly, she went
OL,8,FAWOL repeatedly. She assaulted and
OL,9,Fmade threats to others. Decisions to
OL,10,Fgrant leave were made repeatedly
OL,11,Fdespite this clear escalating pattern
OL,12,Fof risk.
OL,14,F"Roger was not failed by one agency
OL,15,Falone. Without formal learning and
OL,16,Fenforceable recommendations directed
OL,17,Fat the NHS, we fear that the systemic
OL,18,Ffailures exposed by this inquest will
OL,19,Fremain only partially addressed.
OL,21,F"Roger deserved better than this."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/20
