OL,4,Cpatient 'failed on every level', says
OL,5,Cfamily
OL,7,FGreater Manchester Assistant Chief
OL,8,FConstable Steph Parker said: "On
OL,9,Fbehalf of GMP I want to apologise to
OL,10,FRoger's family for our failure to
OL,11,Fproperly pass key information to other
OL,12,Fpartners before and after he was
OL,13,Fkilled.
OL,15,F"It is to our great regret that this
OL,16,Ftragic incident could ever have
OL,17,Fhappened, and that our processes at
OL,18,Fthis time were not more thorough to
OL,19,Feffectively work with partners."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/20
