OL,7,FParker said the force accepted the
OL,8,Fcoroner's findings and is immediately
OL,9,Fintroducing a new mental health
OL,10,Fmonitoring and handover form which it
OL,11,Fwill look to share nationally
OL,13,FDetective Chief Superintendent Laura
OL,14,FKoscikiewicz, head of crime at South
OL,15,FYorkshire Police, said: "We fully
OL,16,Faccept the learning opportunities
OL,17,Fhighlighted during the inquest and
OL,18,Fthat changes should have been made
OL,19,Fsooner around the handover of missing
OL,20,Fpeople to other agencies, to ensure
OL,21,Fkey information is passed on.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/20
