OL,7,F"We are sorry that these processes
OL,8,Fwere not in place at the time and we
OL,9,Fare committed to delivering continuous
OL,10,Fimprovement around missing people
OL,11,Finvestigations to ensure this does not
OL,12,Fhappen again."
OL,14,FKaren Howell, chief executive of
OL,15,FGreater Manchester Mental Health NHS
OL,16,FFoundation Trust (GMMH) said: "On
OL,17,Fbehalf of GMMH, I want to say how very
OL,18,Fsorry we are to Mr Leadbeater's
OL,19,Ffamily, friends and everyone affected
OL,20,Fby his.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/20
